attributes.title: eN Effect: Deeper Insights by Nithyananda (Morning Satsang)  14 Jan 2011
attributes.description: Living enlightened master and avatar gives deeper insights into eN-effect during the morning satsang of 14 January 2011. He says what he calls as eN-effect and the result of it being kundalini awakening, the side effects of which are things like levitation and intense blissful state, is authentic and true to the tradition that has been set by enlightened masters like Shiva, Buddha and others. Watch this intense discourse for more details.
